{"tid":465004,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【雙11爆買】僅12分鐘 天貓第一單上海收到貨","createTime":"2017-11-11T06:08:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-11T12:31:35.000Z","uid":84436,"like":8,"dislike":103,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"4a45f45ddec89f02f7c2da59c5be94ffb4740de9","tid":465004,"uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T06:08:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171111/57445392\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171111%2F57445392&d=CeERpCKrFVwiV386tkw2u10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=72ca28de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171111%2F57445392&h=8391ec7f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171111/57445392</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據中新網報道，在雙11啟動12分鐘，就完成了當天第一個訂單的簽收。上海嘉定區劉先生11日零時點後在天貓超市購買了零食，菜鳥智慧物流從離他就近的倉庫發貨，花12分鐘送到。<br />\n<br />\n今年天貓雙11第一單誕生在上海嘉定區朱橋鎮。劉先生早早在購物車內添加了雀巢咖啡、餅乾、堅果等零食。零點剛過，他就完成了付款。訂單通過菜鳥智能倉配系統，由機器人和流水線根據算法自動完成揀選和包裝。4分鐘內商品就被貼上菜鳥電子面單後從倉庫發出，12分18秒簽收成功。當快遞員敲響劉先生的家門時，他還在繼續血拚。<br />\n據悉，往年雙11，行業內配送快的商品往往是大小家電，因為作為標品規格統一，許多都不需要二次包裝，揀選和出庫都很高效。但是今年，天貓雙11實現了快消品的極速配送。以雀巢這樣的快消品為例，菜鳥多渠道共享庫存，發貨更加快，加上啟用機械人作業，讓揀貨、發貨的效率和準確性都大幅提高。<br />\n菜鳥網絡總裁萬霖表示，雙11是對物流的大挑戰，希望通過技術和協同，加速實現「全國24小時、全球72小時必達」。"},{"pid":"4f603671477354b6caad1df025abb563d742bb5b","tid":465004,"uid":90863,"like":299,"dislike":4,"score":295,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T06:33:22.000Z","msg":"咁代表佢落街買可能仲快"},{"pid":"c8674f8d4d32fd0944a9e9a1f4f58c919931e3db","tid":465004,"uid":389,"like":3,"dislike":20,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T06:50:47.000Z","msg":"乜Q機械人AI<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇死佢人手執比佢然後送貨"},{"pid":"ac514aa7c3cf3d4616e28850842b7d86a3f7743c","tid":465004,"uid":73340,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T06:55:05.000Z","msg":"下年一定十分內<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19b754cb98a9810b20a19db3109d9ecb2ad886de","tid":465004,"uid":14719,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T06:56:44.000Z","msg":"送去格離單位二 三分鐘都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76074037a4ebb5d49afe5793493663c2d25f09db","tid":465004,"uid":17646,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T06:56:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁代表佢落街買可能仲快</blockquote><br />\n落街買無得平"},{"pid":"2f7dcce65df9e0218e3955180722b873fa6f200f","tid":465004,"uid":17646,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T06:57:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜Q機械人AI<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇死佢人手執比佢然後送貨</blockquote><br />\n人手可以咁撚快咩?"},{"pid":"997ee9a93dcdc373c3c6cdf0eb43dd351d2e50ed","tid":465004,"uid":9348,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T06:57:58.000Z","msg":"關你撚事咩毒果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1c500b731603a21129515e5e8f89e7a0d371e1a","tid":465004,"uid":17646,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T07:05:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>關你撚事咩毒果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n收左廣告錢點會唔關蘋果事"},{"pid":"91c24d3dee763374b6c934d27c2d0d7a09713590","tid":465004,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T07:19:49.000Z","msg":"香港網購？"},{"pid":"07e0678b584b55c989ab0f177b27c5fbdce83c0b","tid":465004,"uid":54132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T07:27:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>關你撚事咩毒果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4f49bcb48d35363f8ad68a7765fdb39502c511b","tid":465004,"uid":71624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T07:52:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>關你撚事咩毒果<